PLACEHOLDER: Replace this file with your Open Graph image
Size: 1200x630 pixels (required for social media)
Format: JPG
File name: og-image.jpg

This image appears when someone shares your website on:
- Facebook
- LinkedIn
- Twitter
- WhatsApp

Design tips:
1. Include school name and logo
2. Add tagline: "Where Every Mind Belongs"
3. Use brand colors (teal: #2a9d8f, blue: #4a90c4)
4. Keep text large and readable
5. Avoid small details

Tools to create:
- Canva.com (free templates)
- Figma
- Adobe Spark
